---
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-container">
		<div class="footer-grid">
			<div class="footer-brand">
				<span class="brand-name">{SITE_TITLE}</span>
				<p>데이터와 AI로 분석하는 대한민국 부동산 트렌드 및 투자 전략</p>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-links">
				<h5>Resources</h5>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/blog">Market Reports</a></li>
					<li><a href="/blog">Daily Briefings</a></li>
					<li><a href="/about">Methodology</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-links">
				<h5>Company</h5>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
					<li><a href="mailto:contact@estateintel.local">Contact</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-social">
				<h5>Follow Us</h5>
				<div class="social-icons">
					<a href="#" class="material-symbols-outlined">public</a>
					<a href="#" class="material-symbols-outlined">rss_feed</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-bottom">
			<p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} {SITE_TITLE}. All rights reserved. Data provided by MOLIT.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		width: 100%;
		background: #f4f6f8;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
		padding: 64px 24px 32px;
		margin-top: 64px;
	}
	.footer-container {
		max-width: 1280px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.footer-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 48px;
		margin-bottom: 48px;
	}
	.brand-name {
		font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
		font-size: 24px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--primary);
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
	}
	.footer-brand p {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: var(--muted);
		max-width: 300px;
	}
	h5 {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 14px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--primary);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-bottom: 24px;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}
	ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}
	ul li {
		margin-bottom: 12px;
	}
	ul li a {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: var(--body);
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}
	ul li a:hover {
		color: var(--secondary);
	}
	.social-icons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 16px;
	}
	.social-icons a {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 20px;
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.social-icons a:hover {
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	.footer-bottom {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
		padding-top: 32px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.footer-bottom p {
		font-size: 13px;
		color: var(--muted);
	}
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		}
	}
	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 32px;
		}
	}
</style>
